posts.body:
>>2073bc92-e81a-4540-b5c5-5529e2a2704b
The clunkyness of the interface and the exctra steps required to browse ZeroNet will keep normalfags away. At least for a while. 

On the other hand, the old 8chan did work better. Also, you didn't need seeders to keep a file online. The central server did all the work for you. This is both a blessing and a curse.

>>0c460d86-e205-4598-816a-ab94c5a61be7
Consider this: 
Without code-monkey's tweet most of us would not be here. This "look, a wierd 8chan clone we didn't make" was, or became part of the plan, be that for good or ill.

>>48fff1b8-916f-43a5-8b9d-b0ef14df6f34
I'm not saying it's good or bad. I'm just saying neither shills or polaks seem to comment on the cattle-herding effects of the tweet.  How did you figure out about 08chan? Most likely, whomever you've heard it from heard it from that tweet.

--------------------------
All you turbofaggots flodding the board with images like there's no fucking tomorrow.

Seriously, if you want to seed what's important don't post images/files unless they're important. Stick to text. We're back in the 2-chan era now fellas. Without daddy Server to subsidize it, bandwidth and storage space don't grow on trees.
------------------------

>>62423d78-221c-4956-b7b7-95b1cb4b8aca
Your download speed is proportional to the upload speed and capability of the seeders. Yeah, there's probably some brain damage, but shit's impressive that it works. Also, it's not fully decentralized, the owner of the site can still delete shit if he wants (whatever updates he makes have priority in the 'hive mind'). Anyway, there's a reason I recommend old-style posting.

>>bfdc4f6d-b1de-4add-bd93-0b1afcca2d49
We can counter-meme it.
Eg: Zero-net/08chan is a virus/Trojan/honeypot. 

People are already doing it here, might as well do it somewhere useful.

posts.subject: Any working chans remaining on the open net?
posts.body: This place is quiet as fuck. Since 8chan went down, the remaining pol-aks must have gone somewhere.  So, either they went to 4chan to burn, or some other places. But, 4chan aside, I haven't been able to find any chans with a pol-board.  Are there any? Do you still use chans on the open net?
